import React from "react";

class ProductList extends React.Component {
    constructor(props) {
        super(props);
        this.state = {};
    }

    render() {
        return ( <
            React.Fragment >
            <
            h1 className = "p-3" > ProductList < /h1> <
            section className = "Container " >
            <
            div className = "row" >
            <
            div className = "col" >
            <
            div className = "card" >
            <
            div className = "card-body" >
            <
            p className = "text text-success " > Product List < /p>  <
            div className = "card-inputs" >
            <
            div className = "card-footer" >
            <
            div className = "form-group" >
            <
            /div> < /
            div > <
            /div> < /
            div > <
            /div> < /
            div > <
            /div> < /
            section >


            <
            /React.Fragment>
        );
    }
}

export default ProductList;
